    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated VANOS system. The chassis integrity is guaranteed via a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a precision-aligned suspension utilizing OEM+ components. Every mechanical system is in peak operational state, including a recent rod bearing service and a cooling system overhaul. The paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero orange peel or clear coat failure, while the cockpit retains its factory-fresh tactile feedback and Nappa leather integrity. A truly turn-key, investment-grade driver's car.",
